Paper: hep-th/9212098

Date: 1992-12-16

Title: The Polyakov action on the supertorus

Authors: Jean-Pierre Ader and Hamid Kachkachi

Comments: 15 pages LaTex

Journal-ref: Class. Quant. Grav. 10 (1993) 417-428

A consistent method for obtaining a well-defined Polyakov action on thesupertorus is presented. This method uses the covariantization of derivativeoperators and enables us to construct a Polyakov action which is globallydefined.